Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.39,0:00:45.75,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}どうして僕らは出逢ったんだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.76,0:00:49.02,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}数字なんかじゃ証明できない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.09,0:00:52.70,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}どんな歴史も色褪せるような
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.75,0:00:55.13,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}神秘のディスカバリー
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.25,0:00:58.91,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}ピタリとハマった　天声のパスワード
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.94,0:01:02.08,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}宇宙Levelのシンパシー
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.12,0:01:09.93,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}創造紀元の胎動が聞こえているか…？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.04,0:01:11.51,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Burning through the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.57,0:01:16.29,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}極上の未来を作り出そう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.37,0:01:23.20,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}争鳴の空へと飴色のジェットで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.21,0:01:28.33,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}未熟な夢積み込んだらフルスロットル
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.35,0:01:35.30,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}翔ぼう！想いのままに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.27,0:01:45.27,OPJ1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Touch and go, Catch the sun!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,=================OPC=================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.20,0:00:39.25,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Touch and go, Catch the sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.39,0:00:45.75,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}为何我们相会于此？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.76,0:00:49.02,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}单纯的数字是无法证明的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.09,0:00:52.70,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}能让一切历史黯然无色的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.75,0:00:55.13,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}神秘大发现
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.25,0:00:58.91,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}恰巧合适的 启示的密码
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.94,0:01:02.08,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}那是宇宙级的交感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.12,0:01:09.93,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}你能听见创造新纪元的胎动吗…？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.04,0:01:11.51,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Burning through the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.57,0:01:16.29,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}创造出至高的未来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.37,0:01:23.20,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}乘上琥珀色的喷气飞机 向着争鸣的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.21,0:01:28.33,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}载满不成熟的梦想全力踩下油门
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.35,0:01:35.30,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}飞翔吧！一如所愿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.27,0:01:45.27,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Touch and go, Catch the sun!
