Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.73,0:22:21.66,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur2}一意向前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.77,0:22:24.87,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur2}就像在数着天上的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.79,0:22:30.10,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur2}永不消失的羁绊正在绽放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.39,0:22:37.54,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur2}梦想已然起步 它指引着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.75,0:22:41.91,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur2}倾注着梦想 描绘出这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.03,0:22:47.13,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur2}这份想要守护什么的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.25,0:22:52.52,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur2}定然会给我面对一切的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.73,0:22:55.75,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur2}因为我想直白地传达给你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.93,0:22:58.78,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur2}唱歌吧 啦啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.00,0:23:01.98,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur2}接受吧 啦啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.18,0:23:06.19,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur2}在心底发光发热 永不会被忘却的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.20,0:23:08.62,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur2}是你给我的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.68,0:23:11.63,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur2}一起来 啦啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.66,0:23:14.60,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur2}许愿吧 啦啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.82,0:23:18.63,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur2}紧握的手儿是如此温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.78,0:23:24.08,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur2}我永远也不会松开
